{"tid":2272616,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男生認藏士巴拿索帶 鄭念慈判處160小時社會服務令","createTime":"2020-11-05T07:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T11:35:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"00d115258c5f98cdded2a42e0a4799986747a6c3","tid":2272616,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:23:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F11024&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4KRE6aJPUBN7WNjl4CDefRw%3D&h=fcd8f568\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11024</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第二庭<br />\n#鄭念慈裁判官<br />\n🕝14:30<br />\n👤楊(21)🛑已還押20日 🔥#判刑 (#1027旺角 管有適合作非法用途的工具)<br />\n<br />\n160小時社會服務令<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n判詞：<br />\n<br />\n你22歲，得到家人關心，與父母關係良好，基層出身，但成績良好，能進入大學，現在畢業了，有機會晉身醫護行業做物理治療。<br />\n<br />\n本案有一定嚴重性管有物品可做非法用途使用，包括士巴拿可以做刑事毀壞用途，拆除欄杆；還有索帶，可以將拆下的物品索緊作為堵路之用，我認為案件的確有一定嚴重性，我不能忽略兩個原則，懲罰和阻嚇，不但阻嚇你，也阻嚇其他人仿效。<br />\n<br />\n你年紀相對輕，案發時更年輕，背景良好，沒有刑事定罪前科，看過所有求情信，文件後，認為重犯機會不高，坦白認罪是後悔重要的指標，不但如此，我看完所有求情信，家人求情信，你法律代表的說法，似乎你悔意不但明白自己犯罪，還明白為何自己會犯法，你說明白到社會有不同的人，有不同立場，顯然你犯法前沒有深入考慮。父母的 求情信，除了不斷讚揚，也提及，你說到羈留期間你有機會與警察交談，理解雙方立場差異，我覺得你不但認罪，還明白到犯法背後的根源，因為你沒有考慮到其他人有其他立場其他責任有他們的 工作。報告中顯示，你真的學到了這一課，你知道自己立場，知道需要考慮其他人。相信重犯機會不高。<br />\n<br />\n判刑需要懲罰阻嚇，還要考慮更生，我接納你是真誠的悔意。所有因素最好權衡，我認為社會服務令方式處理本案最為恰當。<br />\n<br />\n160小時社會服務令是適當的判刑。如果你不做，會即時監禁。社會服務令也配合你就本案已經被羈押20天。"},{"pid":"2909ed405408163d87932acdbea922af1e25c533","tid":2272616,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9628097bb996b0177134161aece9f834d2ab18db","tid":2272616,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28711ab28dca7e931d173ffb6518d373f811004","tid":2272616,"uid":39072,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:29:58.000Z","msg":"唔洗坐都算係咁"},{"pid":"896f2ab8a537a289d4f7ed6bfc3d7440fabab19a","tid":2272616,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:34:31.000Z","msg":"管有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb9d6e85e78dc377cc08f36fb63f4620ab58dd6","tid":2272616,"uid":293543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:34:39.000Z","msg":"你說到羈留期間你有機會與警察交談，理解雙方立場差異<br />\n<br />\n因為咁先無判咁重咋"},{"pid":"b2668aad6db99a5fa7d796fdb71d12fb2df4bd54","tid":2272616,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d45bbd6cad0c8fc7b7f80e360f02d787b6fbd2f","tid":2272616,"uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a28711ab28dca7e931d173ffb6518d373f811004","tid":2272616,"uid":39072,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:29:58.000Z","msg":"唔洗坐都算係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:05:16.000Z","msg":"本身坐咗20日喇"},{"pid":"a052a54119b245bcc24dcf66dfeac25cde5e5c1b","tid":2272616,"uid":55162,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a28711ab28dca7e931d173ffb6518d373f811004","tid":2272616,"uid":39072,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:29:58.000